Package: mantid-term
Architecture: any
Depends: libgtk-3-0, libgnutls30, libpcre2-8-0, python3, python3-gi, python3-yaml, gobject-introspection
Description: fully keyboard-controllable terminal inspired by termite
  *Mantid* is a xterm-compatible terminal emulator based on Vte-ng,
  similar to termite. Keybindings and appearance can be defined via
  a configuration file in yaml format.
